---
title: Miso Maple–Glazed Salmon with Sweet Potato Jumble
description: PB&J, ham and pineapple, fries and milkshakes... these are some of our favorite sweet-salty combos and we’re adding miso and maple syrup to that “swalty” list. Here, we top juicy salmon with a miso maple glaze and, since we think you’ll like it so much, there’s extra to drizzle over the accompanying jumble of roasted sweet potato, zucchini, bell pepper, and onion. #glazefordays
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/6631310e0fc5c011176b0d04-bbf5bfae.jpeg
